<h2 id="comments">Letters to the editor</h2>

<div id="c1">
<p>The powerbook battery to get is the Newer Technology NuPower Powerbook replacement.  I bought it just before heading to StartupSchool and it saved me.  I regularly get 4+ hrs on my 12" 1 ghz powerbook (up from 35 mins with the old one).</p>


<p class="posted">posted by <a rel="nofollow" href="http://adamkravetz.com">Adam</a>
 on 2005-11-21T22:24:42 <a href="wishlist#c1" rel="bookmark">#</a></p>
</div>
